# Documentation Creator

After implementation, sync human-readable docs with behavior.

## When to update

- Behavior, interfaces, or architecture changed
- New endpoints, collections, env vars, or user flows

## File header format

```typescript
/**
 * filename.ts
 * @author: @gatahcha
 * @date: YYYY-MM-DD
 * @description: ...
 */
```

First line of file (optional): `// public/scripts/api.ts`

## Class / function TSDoc

- Class: list key methods
- Function: `@param`, `@returns`, behavioral note

## Architecture docs

- API changes → `documentation/ENDPOINT_ARCHITECTURE.md`
- Mongo → `documentation/MONGO_DATA_LAYER.md`
- Setup → `README.md`

Check in before considering task complete.

## Deployment note

On-prem staging/prod; provide staging validation checklist when user asks.
